_sText:
This is a small map for low populations (below 10), but can hold more than 20 players. There are camping spots for those who love camping, and barricading spots for those who love barricading. This can be an alternative to zm_lila_panic during low population timings.
I have ensured that every spot is useful, so every space in this small map area can be fully utilised.

-64/64 spawnpoints
-Cubemaps (compiled)
-LDR
-Compiled in Normal BSP, VIS and RAD
-Good FPS

Join FireWaLL // Zombie at 206.212.243.130:27015 to try out the map and other FireWaLL maps, or visit our website at www.FireWaLLCS.net/forums.
